==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Turrethead
<hw>Tur"ret*head</hw>. <def>an attachment fitted to a lathe or other
machinery which holds a variety of tools which can act on the object
being worked, and which are interchangeable by a pivoting motion, thus
allowing efficient performance of multiple operations; -- also called a
<altname>turret</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Turret lathe</ent>⟦br⟧
